* Pumping young but well built muscles the tiny form of Diana ran straight 
towards the large metallic form of the Maximal city, finding that her 
scanners could only pick up 4 mail objects...only 2 of them containing spark 
signatures.
#1 was the city itself and the large ship that was hovering above it, #3 and 
4 were the two figures which stood just outside what seeemed like the front 
gates.
Nearing the largest of the figures ( azureblade ), Diana dared to turn her 
head and look behind as she ran. Looking at Rion.*

" Come O.....!!!!"

* It was almost instant but there was very little pain as the fur covered 
form of the kitten Diana came into solid contact with the back of the great 
dragon's foot.*

" OOF!!"
